[normal]In summary, The IFM strongly supports the first tranche of designations.
[normal] We believe that there are lessons to be learnt, that can now be put to good use. 
[normal]Sustainable management and development must be built around accessible robust science operating at the heart of open and frank negotiations, followed by rigorous post-project appraisal with active lesson uptake.  The Institute has a wealth of experience in this field. We look forward to positive engagement in MCZ development in the future. We hope you have found our comments helpful.
[normal]&#xa0;
